			<div class="content" id="post-content-4507435">
									

<p>Thank you to my critters <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;">Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;">plaidypus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyvstvi13" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6004508); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6004508&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="Cyvstvi13" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6004508)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyvstvi13" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6004508); return false;">Cyvstvi13</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sharpembrace" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6032914); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6032914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="SharpEmbrace" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6032914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sharpembrace" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6032914); return false;">SharpEmbrace</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/geckoguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3757542); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3757542&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="geckoguy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3757542)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/geckoguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3757542); return false;">geckoguy</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1989312); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1989312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="Doctor Fullham" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1989312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1989312); return false;">Doctor Fullham</a></span>. If I missed you, and you want to be added, please let me know.</p>
<p>If you'd like to read more of my work, please <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/malycegraves-author">visit my Author's Page</a>.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Attributions</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Forward, concept, &amp; overall structure copied from <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/an-anthropological-approach-to-sarkicism-case-study-02-the-d">An Anthropological Approach to Sarkicism</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582221729" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;">Metaphysician</a></span>, which is licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0</p>
<p>I created the Darkwater Lodge sigil, and it is licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/74af71ee-a3aa-431e-aa4b-d42407eb022a">Celebrant</a></li>
<li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Scarification_in_Africa_in_the_early_1940s.jpg">Karcist Enitan</a></li>
<li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/997c39a4-7586-4ff8-9136-f45439fb911f">The Black Flesh</a></li>
<li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/2f28047c-e5c5-4f13-9546-5bb1e07d578d">Idol of Nyam(b)e</a></li>
<li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Nubian_woman,_Anglo-Egyptian_Sudan_LCCN2001705677.tif">Volutaar Enu</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Naman lives, and is within 20 years of Apotheosis, or what he believes will be Apotheosis.</p>
<p>The raid made it clear that he couldn't hide in the woods anymore, he needed somewhere else. <em>La Rue Macabre</em> was just that, but Naman was a violent man with a violent past. He was willing to put that aside, but the leadership there wouldn't budge.</p>
<p>So, Naman became Enu and Enitan.</p>
<p>The power from the Archons is tainted, but all of his family has a bit of it. So Naman is using the Black Flesh to filter the corruption through the bodies of his descendants. He merges their physical with the spirits of their ancestors, and slowly sucks the spark from them.</p>
<p>Enough life, enough flesh, enough age. Power grows, but slowly.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

